{
  "stem": "10353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they didn't like it, but they didn't have very much to offer for me in support.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, I was already my 18th year, and so I had to fend for myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had already acquired the knowledge of salesmanship in the textile business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went up to Budapest for better-- to-- to seek something better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You get lost-- in a bigger city, you get lost.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, while anti-Semitism existed, and you knew that existed, but you could sort of mingle more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were great restrictions by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have eliminated all the Jewish art, like actors and actresses couldn't appear, Jewish actresses couldn't appear, and Jewish music wouldn't be played openly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Jews organized themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they created their own theaters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As for myself, I-- I couldn't become a salesman, per se, because like I told you, because of the numerus clausus, in this respect-- only 6%.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like for instance, if I want to work in a store, they have to have at least two, three non-Jewish salesmen before I could hold a job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's random percentages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how life was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we lived modestly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in number 21 [NON-ENGLISH]-- which is-- in English, you would call it Elizabeth Road or Boulevard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, I just rented a room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived on my own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, because I have finished Romanian school only, and I only finished some public schools, I tried to excel in Hungarian, and I took the equivalent of four-year high school, night courses.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I also took courses in languages, so I studied English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I studied German, studied-- study Spanish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was more into studies during my spare time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And this is how life was going on until 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived a fairly normal--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not open-- well, I belonged to an organization prior, and I-- I-- we'll sort of backtrack a little bit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their first inclination that we got about the Polish Jews was in January of 1941, when a train of Polish refugees were passing by our city, and on their way to Constanta, to a Romanian port through the Black Sea, a pantheon-- on their way to Palestine, through that time, Palestine.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was a Betar at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I belonged to an organization, Betar, a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as young kids, we were told that we have to go out to the train to-- to take some food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKS] And we saw all these Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING] And that was the first time we knew what was wrong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked to the people, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They cried, and they left their homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remembered that we gave-- we gave a piece of chocolate to one man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said that, I owned a chocolate factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a year before they came to me, and they asked me for help, and-- and I declined.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now, I take a chocolate from you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he cried very bitterly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is, I remember, I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we lived with this start all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this was going on until 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I lived in Budapest, and until the beginning of March, March 4th, I believe it was, that all of a sudden the German army swooped down on Budapest on a Sunday afternoon, and they occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Within-- I'll have to backtrack again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And within one week, all the anti-Jewish laws were [BACKGROUND NOISE] handed out with a yellow star to be affixed under the threat of death.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a Jew could not go on a train any more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And even if I wanted to go home, I couldn't go home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a Jew couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a certain curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only once, only once did I go back during the time that I left Suta Mare.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But prior to that, and like I said, I'll backtrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1942, there was a great influx of Slovak Jewish refugees that because they had the noose, again, tightened up on 'em, and that [NON-ENGLISH], the Nazi Governor took over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jews were fleeing into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as it happens, my sister was a little bit older than I am.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was living in Suta Mare, and she was with a committee that was making documents for these Slovak Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she-- they got caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They got caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister got caught with the whole committee, got caught.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they searched our house in Suta Mare, and they found some correspondence from me in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
